data.description: Welcome home in Crown Colony, perfectly sitting on the edge of the cul-de-sac. Wonderful fenced in backyard, with lots of space and privacy. Open concept ready for entertaining a large get together or your own personal setting.  The wood burning fireplace will be an inviting center point for the upcoming season.  Recent improvements new HVAC, energy efficient windows and super bonus of tankless water heater.  Schedule a showing today and get ready to call this place home.
